  DISEASES & MEDICINE
============================================================

Disease:     HIV/AIDS
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    HIV
Transmission:Sexual contact, blood
Symptoms:    Flu-like; then AIDS symptoms
Treatment:   Antiretroviral therapy (ART)
Deaths/yr:   0.65M
Vaccine:     No (in development)
Discovered:  1983

Disease:     COVID-19
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    SARS-CoV-2
Transmission:Respiratory droplets
Symptoms:    Fever, cough, loss of smell
Treatment:   Antivirals, supportive care
Deaths/yr:   5.0M
Vaccine:     Yes (mRNA vaccines)
Discovered:  2019

Disease:     Dengue
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    Dengue virus
Transmission:Aedes mosquito
Symptoms:    Fever, severe joint pain, rash
Treatment:   Supportive care, fluids
Deaths/yr:   0.04M
Vaccine:     Yes (for previously infected)
Discovered:  1779

